SUMMARY:2026 Lancaster Cool Schools Mobile Polar Plunge
DESCRIPTION:Join us for the Lancaster Cool Schools Polar Plunge on Friday\, March 13 at JP McCaskey High School to experience the magic of Plunge and support Special Olympics Pennsylvania athletes by jumping into our mobile plunge unit – Bear Force One! \nEvery dollar raised helps support vital programming for individuals with intellectual and developmental disabilities\, ensuring quality training\, competition\, and leadership opportunities for students at new and exsisting Special Olympics PA Unified Champion Schools! \nPlungers commit to “Freezin’ for a Reason” and raise a minimum of $35 to dip a toe\, wade\, or jump into icy waters. \nSo\, create your team and join thousands of plungers around the state in making a splash to support our athletes \nCLICK HERE TO LEARN MORE 
URL:https://sdlancaster.org/event/2026-lancaster-cool-schools-mobile-polar-plunge/
CATEGORIES:All Events
END:VEVENT
