SUMMARY:Philly Bike Expo via the Schuylkill River Trail - 30/35 F - RSVP R
 equired
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\nJoin our annual casual ri
 de to the Philly Bike Expo at the Philadelphia Convention Center. We will 
 ride mostly on the paved Schuylkill River Trail and turn off onto Race Str
 eet riding city streets to our destination. We will be using the Manayunk 
 towpath for a couple of miles which is not paved. Road bikes can be used o
 n this section\, but it could be a little rough.\n\nThis ride is cross-pos
 ted with the Wilmington Biking Rails to Trails Group. Option\, for those w
 ho wish\, coming back ride the new extension South on the trail.\n\nTicket
 s are $25 at the door or they can be purchased prior to the date for $20 h
 ere: https://phillybikeexpo.com/events/2026-philly-bike-expo\n\nOther expo
  information can be found here: https://phillybikeexpo.com\n\nWe park our 
 bikes inside the Convention Center using their complimentary valet bike pa
 rking. After we visit the exhibits\, we will walk across the street to the
  Reading Terminal Market for lunch before returning to Conshohocken.\n\nRa
 in date is the next day\, Sunday\, March 15th.\n\nHelmets are mandatory. N
 o ear buds. Please bring water and a basic repair kit (spare tube\, tire l
 evers\, pump/CO2 inflator).\n\nTo eliminate passing around a pen and paper
  waiver\, we require LBC Club membership and Meetup RSVP below to join thi
 s ride.\n\nBeing on Meetup does not mean you are a club member. [Join here
 ](https://www.lancasterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=60&club_id=257148
 ).\n\nYour RSVP is your agreement to abide by the club's [Code of Conduct]
 (https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=2571
 48&module_id=323984) \,\n[Rules of the Road](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpr
 ess.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=325159) \, and [R
 ide Waiver](https://lancasterbikeclub.net/docs.ashx?id=454318)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-bicycle-club/events/3130212
 51/
