SUMMARY:Coffee and Critique Club
DESCRIPTION:Critique\, Community and Coffee! \n\n\n\nCritique Club is a welcoming space for artists of all levels — from beginners to established professionals — to bring in their artwork for feedback and discussion. The club is not just about receiving critique; it’s also an opportunity to engage thoughtfully with fellow artists\, share perspectives\, and grow together through open conversation about each other’s work.  \n\n\n\nWe hope you will join us on the Second Saturday of each month for coffee\, critique and community! \n\n\n\nHeld on the Second Saturday of every month March 14\, April 11\, May 9\, June 13\, July 11… \n\n\n\n10:30AM-12:00PM \n\n\n\nFREE EVENT ALTHOUGH REGISTRATION IS REQUIRED.  www.LancasterArtVault.com \n\n\n\nIt’s requested to only bring one piece to allow for time to be distributed evenly to all participants.
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/coffee-and-critique-club/
