 e/mm-manor-meander-32h/](https://routes.lancasterbikeclub.net/cue/mm-manor
 -meander-32h/)\n\n**This ride is intended for the experienced group rider 
 in good physical condition and capable of maintaining a steady pace. Few s
 tops if any. Riders unable to maintain the pace may be dropped. If unsure 
 if this ride is for you\, it is recommended you try the "A" ride option fi
 rst.**\n\nHelmets are mandatory. No earbuds. Please bring water and a basi
 c repair kit (spare tube\, tire levers\, pump/CO2 inflator).\n\nTo elimina
 te passing around a pen and paper waiver\, we require an LBC Club membersh
 ip and Meetup RSVP below to join this ride.\n\nBeing on Meetup does not me
 an you are a club member. [Join here](https://www.lancasterbikeclub.net/co
 ntent.aspx?page_id=60&club_id=257148).\n\nYour RSVP is your agreement to a
 bide by the club's [Code of Conduct](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/
 content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=323984)\,\n\n[Rules of th
 e Road](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_
 id=257148&module_id=325159)
