SUMMARY:St. Patrick's Day Celebration at grandview
DESCRIPTION:Join us for our annual St Patrick’s Day Celebration on Sunday\, March 15th from 12-5pm! We have green wine\, beer\, slushies and cocktails! We are excited to have Fire in the Glen returning to perform for us from 1:30-4. No tickets required. Tasting room seating is limited and we do not take reservations. We will offer seating in the barrel/tank room for overflow and large parties. Please note that it can be cooler in the barrel room\, so please dress accordingly. Music will be playing in both areas.
URL:https://grandviewwines.com/vineyard-event/st-patricks-day-celebration-at-grandview-3/
LOCATION:Grandview Vineyard\, 1489 Grandview Rd\, Mount Joy\, PA\, 17552\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://grandviewwines.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/St-Pattys-Day.jpg
