SUMMARY:Spring Greening the Lower Susquehanna - Litter Clean Up
DESCRIPTION:Greening the Lower Susquehanna is partnering with the Tri-County Conewago Creek Association to clean up the Hershey Meadow riparian buffer. This is a project that is about 15 years old\, needs the final tree tubes removed\, and litter from flooding and local roadways picked-up. This will be a great opportunity to prevent pollution from reaching the Conewago Creek. Registration coming soon!
URL:https://lancasterwatersheds.org/event/spring-greening-the-lower-susquehanna-litter-clean-up/
LOCATION:Elizabethtown\, PA\, United States
