SUMMARY:Fresh Takes On Jazz: La Orquesta Esa
DESCRIPTION:Sunday March 15th\, 2026\n*EARLY SHOW*\nDoors | 2:30 PM\nShow | 3:00 PM \nGeneral Admission Seating | $23.40 + Fees \n+$3 on All Day of Show Purchases\nStudent tickets generously provided by our sponsors – please call our Box Office at (717) 723 – 8463 to reserve yours.\nNo one turned away for lack of funds. Please contact our Box Office at (717) 723-8463 or email info@mickeysblackbox.com to reserve your tickets now.\nThis event is all ages – 21+ With Valid ID to Drink\nCome hungry! Snacks and light bites will be available at the canteen.\n————————————————–\nPresented by Mickey’s Black Box & Music For Everyone\n————————————————–\nLa Orquesta Esa is a lively 10-piece salsa band led by Gina Benalcazar-Lopez\, a New York City trombonist\, arranger and composer. The band will release its first album this spring. Gina\, 32\, holds a master’s degree from Michigan State.    \nCheck out La Orquesta Esa here!\nWebsite | Instagram | Facebook \nFeaturing a special performance by: Mambojaz Studio \n\n \nTHANK YOU TO OUR SUPPORTERS!\n \n\n\n \nRobert M. Lauman Charitable Foundation \nJohn Swanson \nGaylord and Nadine Poling\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nFarmstead Friends of Jazz\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nRich & Elena Wolman\n\nArt Lumsden\n\n \n \nThe Fresh Takes series would not be possible without the generous support of our community.\n\n————————————————–\n*Ticket Alert* \nTickets for Mickey’s Black Box are sold through TicketMaster\, via our website\, or in person at our Box Office. Any tickets purchased elsewhere will not be honored and we are not responsible for tickets purchased from any 3rd party sellers. Do not google the name of the band to search for tickets. Go to Mickeysblackbox.com ONLY. Mickeysblackbox.com will never direct you anywhere but the official TicketMaster event site. \n\nAll bags are subject are to search upon entry. Tickets are non-refundable\, save for instances in which performances are cancelled by Mickey’s Black Box. For more information about our venue or to make an ADA request\, please visit the FAQ page of our website: https://mickeysblackbox.com/faq/ or call our box office line at (717) 723 – 8463.
URL:https://mickeysblackbox.com/event/fresh-takes-on-jazz-la-orquesta-esa/
LOCATION:Mickey’s Black Box\, 101 Rock Lititz Boulevard\, Lititz\, PA\, 17543\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mickeysblackbox.com/app/uploads/2026/01/Gina-2.jpg
END:VEVENT
