SUMMARY:Worship Night In The Barn at Paradise Station
DESCRIPTION:Experience local live worship in an intimate setting led by local Pastor and Worship Leader Brett Lovern of Mission Church. This free event is open to everyone from all walks of life. Come together to sing songs of praise to our Creator. Worship nights in the Barn are interdenominational and are open to people of all faiths. Come as you are. \nEvent is free. Parking is free. \nDoors open to at 6 o’clock for free coffee and treats in the lower level. \nWorship and teaching begins at 7 o’clock upstairs. Song lyrics will be provided. \n\nCome Explore Our Lancaster Theaters and the Arts\n\n\nLive Theater\nLive Entertainment\nLive Music\n\n\n\nDinner Theaters\nMurder Mysteries\nThings To Do\n\n\n\nArtisan Collectives\nArt Galleries\nEvents Calendar
