SUMMARY:Tuesday Training Ride 25R (A) (20-22 mph)
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\nAverage speed: 18-20mph\n
 \nDue to the race-like style of this ride\, including pacelining at high s
 peeds\, the use of E-bikes is not recommended.\n\n25 mile rolling route:\n
 \nOdd dates: CC Tuesday Fitness Ride Odd Days (25R)\nEven dates: CC Tuesda
 y Fitness Ride Even Days (26R)\n\nFor links to both cues:\n[https://routes
 .lancasterbikeclub.net/?l=7&t&c&mi&k=tuesday%20fitness](https://routes.lan
 casterbikeclub.net/?l=7&t&c&mi&k=tuesday%20fitness)\n\nBring lights as nee
 ded\; Helmets are mandatory\; No ear buds. Please bring water\, and a basi
 c repair kit (spare tube\, tire levers\, pump/CO2 inflator).\n\nHelmets ar
 e mandatory\; No ear buds or audible music playing devices. Please bring w
