SUMMARY:FREE Yoga in the Gallery
DESCRIPTION:Free Community Yoga Class Every Tuesday 6:30-7:30PMMarch 10 – April 14 \n\n\n\nJoin us for a free\, all-levels community yoga class led by Laela Brown\,  Yoga Teacher in Training. This slow-flow\, meditative practice is designed to help you unwind\, move mindfully\, and reconnect with your breath and body in a supportive\, inclusive environment. \n\n\n\nClass Details:Style: Slow Flow / Meditative YogaLevel: Open to all levels—beginners welcomeWhat to Bring: Your own yoga mat and/or towelOptional Props: Yoga blocks or bolsters if you use them \n\n\n\nQuestions?  Please email laelarae26@gmail.com \n\n\n\nPlease note: All participants must pre-register and sign a waiver prior to class.  www.LancasterArtVault.com
