SUMMARY:KickAss: Focusing on Your Health w/ Chelsea
DESCRIPTION:KICKASS is back for March. Join us at The Candy Factory (TCF) for a night of mingling and connecting with other women in our community. Our speaker series fosters a space where we can learn from one another\, support each other’s growth\, and have real conversations about the topics that matter most to our lives\, careers\, and well-being. \nWe’re at an exciting time where conversations about women’s health are more open and public than ever before. This month\, we are thrilled to welcome Chelsea Christmas\, founder of At Her Core Fitness\, to help us dive into this topic. \nRSVP here.
