LAST-MODIFIED:20260219T055535Z
UID:10000771-1773943200-1773957600@mickeysblackbox.com
SUMMARY:Health Rocks!
DESCRIPTION:Thursday March 19th\, 2026\nDoors | 6:00 PM\nShow | 7:00 PM \nGeneral Admission Standing Room | $25.45 + Fees \n+$5 on All Day of Show Purchases\nThis event is all ages – 21+ With Valid ID to Drink\nCome hungry! Snacks and light bites will be available at the canteen.\n————————————————–\nPresented by Music For Everyone & Mickey’s Black Box\n————————————————–\nIn collaboration with Mickey’s Black Box\, Music For Everyone is proud to present Health Rocks!\, a high-energy night of live music celebrating health\, wellness\, and the lifelong joy of rocking & rolling. \nHealth Rocks is an unforgettable rock concert featuring bands made up of musicians ages 50+\, proving that great music (and great health) only gets better with time. Enjoy an exciting lineup of talented cover bands performing classic rock favorites from artists like Chicago\, The Rolling Stones\, Metallica\, Billy Joel\, and more. Health Rocks highlights the powerful connection between music\, vitality\, and community\, because health truly does rock! \nSponsored by: Music For Everyone\, Penn Medicine & Brethren Village\n—————————————————\n*Ticket Alert*  \nTickets for Mickey’s Black Box are sold through TicketMaster\, via our website\, or in person at our Box Office. Any tickets purchased elsewhere will not be honored and we are not responsible for tickets purchased from any 3rd party sellers.  Do not google the name of the band to search for tickets.  Go to Mickeysblackbox.com ONLY. Mickeysblackbox.com will never direct you anywhere but the official TicketMaster event site. \n\nAll bags are subject are to search upon entry. Tickets are non-refundable\, save for instances in which performances are cancelled by Mickey’s Black Box. For more information about our venue or to make an ADA request\, please visit the FAQ page of our website: https://mickeysblackbox.com/faq/ or call our box office line at (717) 723 – 8463.
URL:https://mickeysblackbox.com/event/health-rocks/
LOCATION:Mickey’s Black Box\, 101 Rock Lititz Boulevard\, Lititz\, PA\, 17543\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://mickeysblackbox.com/app/uploads/2026/01/Participant-Flyer-2-e1771480519356.png
END:VEVENT
