X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Zestchef": "https://zestchef.com/class/2736-date-night-seafood-classics/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:zestchef
X-SOURCE:Zestchef
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260320T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260320T200000
DTSTAMP:20260314T000019
CREATED:20251106T225500Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260103T185829Z
UID:10000349-1774029600-1774036800@zestchef.com
SUMMARY:2736 - Date Night: Seafood Classics
DESCRIPTION:Dive into the elegance of coastal cuisine with Chef Josh Noll in this hands-on class dedicated to timeless seafood favorites. Learn essential techniques for working with delicate fish and shellfish – from searing and stuffing to building bright\, balanced sauces.  \nHands on. BYOB. Ages 18 and up. \n\nClams in White Wine\nCrab-Stuffed Shrimp\nPan-Seared Skin-On Salmon\nLemon Beurre Blanc
