SUMMARY:Free Improv Jam!
DESCRIPTION:Have some free fun\, get on our stage\, and do some Improv! Whether you’ve never been on stage or you’ve been in 100 improv shows\, Lancaster Improv Players would love to jam with you! This jam is FREE to attend and is intended to bring together all lovers of improv for an hour of fun. All attendees will be welcome to participate in warmups and 2-3 person scenes at our theater space at 16 South Prince. Jams are an ideal place to meet and perform with new improvisers\, so we hope you come out! Stick around after the jam to catch Their Royal Laziness at 8:30pm Please arrive at 6:45 for sign ups if you plan on performing in the jam! Registering ahead helps us plan the hour\, but does not replace getting there early to sign up. LANCASTER IMPROV PLAYERS is an intimate black box venue located in the heart of Lancaster City. With a capacity of approximately 30 guests\, that means this Lancaster comedy club is entirely front row. Not a nosebleed in sight! After all\, BYOB is just a drink special you never get tired of.
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/free-improv-jam-2/
LOCATION:The Lancaster Improv Theater\, 16 S Prince Str\, Lancaster\, Pennsylvania\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Theatre
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/march-20-jam.jpg
