SUMMARY:Bart Township Building Material & Craft Sale
DESCRIPTION:Date:\nSaturday March 21\, 2026\nSaturday Start time – 8:00 am \nBUILDING MATERIALS\nLots of building materials outside including a wide selection of live edge slab wood. Don’t forget to check out the windows\, doors\, and crafts in the back building or the books in the main fire hall. There will be plenty of food as well. \nCRAFTS * CRAFTS * CRAFTS *\nOur annual craft sale held in conjunction with the Building Material Sale\, will be held in the fire hall with plenty of seating.  Lots of local made crafts and small furniture will be sold. \n\n\n\n\nIf you can’t make it this weekend\, fear not – the mud sale season has just begun.  Check out our full list of upcoming Mud Sales on LancasterPA.com. \nPlease Note: Many of the Fire Companies holding mud sales can always use extra help on the days they receive items and the day of the event.  It takes a LOT of labor to put on a mud sale. \n\n\n 
