UID:14690-1774083600-1774094400@lancasterwatersheds.org
SUMMARY:Spring Greening the Lower Susquehanna - Live Stake and Tree Planting
DESCRIPTION:We will be stabilizing an eroding stream bank by installing live stakes and planting about 100 native trees on a farm. These practical\, low-cost techniques will quickly establish vegetation\, strengthen soils\, and improve water quality.  \n\n\nRegister here. 
URL:https://lancasterwatersheds.org/event/spring-greening-the-lower-susquehanna-live-stake-and-tree-planting/
