SUMMARY:2738 - Midnight Street Market
DESCRIPTION:Step into the energy of a bustling night market with Chef Sophia Dickmyer and explore the irresistible flavors of late-night street food. In this lively hands-on class\, you will learn fun\, crowd-pleasing techniques for recreating your favorite street bites at home. \nHands on. BYOB. Ages 18 and up. *All tickets are priced per person \n\nFried Mozzarella\nStreet Tacos Al Pastor\nCheeseburger Bombs\nDeep-Fried Oreos
