BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Mickeysblackbox": "https://mickeysblackbox.com/event/southern-rock-night/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:mickeysblackbox
X-SOURCE:Mickeysblackbox
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260321T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260321T230000
DTSTAMP:20260313T235921
CREATED:20251219T150035Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260219T055618Z
UID:10000756-1774117800-1774134000@mickeysblackbox.com
SUMMARY:American Rock Revival
DESCRIPTION:Saturday March 21st\, 2026\nDoors | 6:30 PM\nShow | 7:30 PM \nGeneral Admission Standing Room | $27.50 + Fees\nReserved Mezzanine Seating | $27.50 + Fees\nReserved Balcony Seating | $27.50 + Fees \n+$5 on All Day of Show Purchases\nThis event is all ages – 21+ With Valid ID to Drink\nCome hungry! Snacks and light bites will be available at the canteen.\n—————————————————\nPresented by Mickey’s Black Box\n—————————————————\nPreviously billed as “Southern Rock Night” \nJoin Remedy\, Hotlanta\, and Rocks This Way for a night celebrating – you guessed it – Black Crowes\, The Allman Brothers & Aerosmith – playing your favorite classic rock tunes! \nRemedy\nRemedy is a tribute to The Black Crowes \, a southern hard blues-rock jam band. They play The Black Crowes’ tops hits\, fan favorites\, and deep tracks. Remedy performs a high-energy rock n roll set which has earned them a reputation as one of the tri-state’s top tribute acts!  \nHotlanta\nCapturing the creative spirit of the music created by one of the most prolific rock bands in American music history is not something one decides to do without inspiration. In fact\, it is inspiration of the soul that has brought together the members of HOTLANTA.  \nThe grind of the every-day\, the mundane if you will\, is what causes this manifestation of energy and the desire to grab hold of music so special; soul music\, bluesy\, country\, folk\, funk\, down-home gospel inspired music of one of the worlds greatest jam bands ever. “The” jam band it could be said. Experience the emergence of an inspired group of people joining together in a single\, common cause. That being to recreate a feeling\, a vibe\, a spirit of music and love and passion. The music of an American icon\, the music of The Allman Brothers Band. \nRocks This Way\nRocks This Way is a hard-hitting Aerosmith tribute that channels the grit\, swagger\, and soul of the Bad Boys from Boston. With explosive guitar work\, soaring vocals\, and a stadium-ready energy\, they bring the full Aerosmith experience to life. A perfect blend of deep cuts\, mega-hits\, and authentic attitude makes every show feel like the real thing.\n—————————————————\n*Ticket Alert*  \nTickets for Mickey’s Black Box are sold through TicketMaster\, via our website\, or in person at our Box Office. Any tickets purchased elsewhere will not be honored and we are not responsible for tickets purchased from any 3rd party sellers.  Do not google the name of the band to search for tickets.  Go to Mickeysblackbox.com ONLY. Mickeysblackbox.com will never direct you anywhere but the official TicketMaster event site. \n\nAll bags are subject are to search upon entry. Tickets are non-refundable\, save for instances in which performances are cancelled by Mickey’s Black Box. For more information about our venue or to make an ADA request\, please visit the FAQ page of our website: https://mickeysblackbox.com/faq/ or call our box office line at (717) 723 – 8463.
URL:https://mickeysblackbox.com/event/southern-rock-night/
LOCATION:Mickey’s Black Box\, 101 Rock Lititz Boulevard\, Lititz\, PA\, 17543\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mickeysblackbox.com/app/uploads/2025/12/REMEDY-6-IG-1-scaled-e1771480569222.jpg
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Visitlancastercity": "https://visitlancastercity.com/event/play-it-forward-a-benefit-show-for-lancaster-neighbor-fund/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:visitlancastercity
X-SOURCE:Visitlancastercity
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260321T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260321T200000
DTSTAMP:20260312T132647
CREATED:20260304T162551Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260304T162553Z
UID:56696-1774119600-1774123200@visitlancastercity.com
SUMMARY:Play It Forward: A Benefit Show for Lancaster Neighbor Fund
DESCRIPTION:Using improv to build a better world; one ticket at a time! Proceeds from ticket sales will go to the Lancaster Neighbor Fund. \n\n\n\nSince 2015\, Lancaster Improv Players has served our city through laughter; above all\, our mission is to make Lancaster a funnier place. Humor can be a balm in trying times\, and we wouldn’t be the first to say that laughter can be healing. Another important component of building a better world is making sure the programs helping out people in trying times are properly funded\, which is why we are going to PLAY IT FORWARD! \n\n\n\nAll proceeds from this event’s ticket sales will benefit the Lancaster Neighbor Fund. For those unfamiliar with LNF\, they provide direct financial support to immigrants who are vulnerable to deportation from Lancaster County. You can find out more about them and incredible work they do at their website; https://lancasterneighborfund.org/ \n\n\n\nEnjoy an hour of uproarious improv comedy from a curated collection of local talent\, AND build a better world through community care. It’s time to Play It Forward! \n\n\n\nFEATURING: GLORZEBUB and HIPPIE & FRENCHIE! \n\n\n\nBYOB$15 at the door \n\n\n\n(Our tickets are on a sliding scale; you are free to pay at a higher price point to boost the benefit!) \n\n\n\nDue to the size of our theater\, there is a quick turnover time between our scheduled shows. If you purchase tickets to both events on Saturday evening\, you will be asked to wait outside during the break so that the next team can warm up before the audience returns.
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/play-it-forward-a-benefit-show-for-lancaster-neighbor-fund/
LOCATION:Lancaster Improv Players\, 16 S Prince St\, Lancaster\, Pennsylvania\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Community Events,Theatre
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/play-it-forward.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Lancaster Improv Players":MAILTO:kate@lancasterimprovplayers.org
END:VEVENT
