DESCRIPTION:The Warwick Democratic Committee meets monthly to discuss upco
 ming elections\, meet local candidates for office\, plan volunteer actions
  and get-out-the-vote events\, and more. All local Democrats are welcome t
 o attend! **LOCATION.** Meetings take place in the **Lititz Library Commun
 ity Room**. As you approach the front entrance of the Library\, turn to yo
 ur right and enter through the double French doors. **NEED A RIDE?** Just 
 reply to your confirmation email and let us know. We're happy to connect
