SUMMARY:2740 - American Steakhouse: Tableside Classics
DESCRIPTION:Step into the golden age of dining with Chef Joe Hall for an elegant\, hands-on experience inspired by the theater of the classic American steakhouse. Learn to prepare timeless dishes that once defined tableside service\, from bold\, aromatic sautés to flame-kissed desserts. This immersive class combines refined technique with a touch of showmanship\, bringing sophistication and flair to your home cooking. \nHands on. BYOB. Ages 18 and up. \n\nCaesar Salad from Scratch\nRosemary Salt & Parmigiano Fingerling Potatoes\nSteak Diane\nCherries Jubilee
