SUMMARY:Tech Lancaster Meetup
DESCRIPTION:Tech Lancaster Meetups\nWe will be upstairs in "The Sanctuary"
  - when you walk in the main entrance just head up the stairs! We will hav
 e signs as you walk in to guide you.\nPizza is provided free upstairs. Bee
 r/wine/soda/etc at the bar downstairs!\n\nThis months speakers:\n**Zach Fe
 dor - MacGyvered Microphones**\nExploring the science of sound as I scrap 
 together some studio equipment with little more than some magnets and a st
 ick of gum.\n\n**Tyler Golden - Fun with Sensors: Tracking Beers Poured on
  St. Patrick's Day**\nTyler will present his latest iteration of a yearly 
 hobby project - tracking drafts poured at the local pub on St. Patrick's D
 ay. Using inexpensive sensors and microcontroller boards\, he’ll demonst
 rate how to measure the amounts being poured\, stream the data in real tim
 e\, and visualize the flow on a public dashboard.\n\nTypical schedule of e
 vents:\n\n6:30 PM Doors Open/Pizza/Mingle\n\n7:00 PM Introduction/Announce
 ments\n\n7:05 PM First Speaker\n\n7:35 PM Break\n\n7:45 PM Speaker 2\n\n8:
 15 PM End
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/tech-lancaster-meetups/events/3131187
 96/
