LAST-MODIFIED:20260313T150349Z
UID:38960-1774551600-1774558800@candyissweet.com
SUMMARY:The Indie Journalist Meetup w/ Jason
DESCRIPTION:Join us for the Indie Journalist Meetup at The Candy Factory (TCF)\, 342 N. Queen St.\, Lancaster. \nA meetup for independent journalists covering news\, events\, culture\, and lifestyle while navigating the creator economy in Lancaster and surrounding areas. All creators welcome: podcasters\, freelance writers\, bloggers\, YouTubers\, livestreamers\, and more! \nOur mission is to create a space to gather in real life\, to discuss the rewards and challenges of bringing authentic news and information to the Lancaster community\, and to encourage participants to collaborate and share knowledge when appropriate to strengthen our local information ecosystem. \nEvery 4th Thursday. Full details here!
URL:https://candyissweet.com/event/the-indie-journalist-meetup-w-jason/2026-03-26/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://candyissweet.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Screenshot-2026-03-13-at-10.50.15-AM.png
