UID:10042804-1774569600-1774742399@lancasterpa.com
SUMMARY:Gap Fire Company Sale
DESCRIPTION:2026 Gap Fire Company Sale\nOur 50th Annual fire company “mud sale” consignment auction is being held on Friday evening March 27th and Saturday March 28th. \nAs in past years\, it will be held at 836 Houston Run Drive\, Gap on the grounds of Lancaster County Showcase. Please enter from the Route 30 and Newport Rd entrance (across from the Rutter’s convenience store/gas station). There will be limited on-site parking within a 1/4 mile\, while the remainder of the parking will be a 1/2 mile away with a shuttle school bus to bring you to the sale grounds. There will also be limited handicap parking spaces with a placard. \nThe receiving dates and times to bring your consigned or donated items are as follows: Wed. 3/25: 10 AM to 7 PM\, Thurs. 3/26: 8 AM to 7 PM\, Friday 3/27: 8 AM to 3:00 PM. All items to be consigned are to be brought to the sale location at 836 Houston Run Drive. \nNotice: No poultry equipment\, tires\, hazardous equipment\, TVs\, computers\, used appliances\, used sofas\, box lots\, barrels or broken furniture. Gap Fire Company and the receiving attendants reserve the right to reject or accept any items. \nA Variety of food & drinks will be available throughout the day for all to enjoy! \n\nIf you can’t make it this weekend\, check out or full list of upcoming Mud Sales on LancasterPA.com.
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/gap-fire-company-sale/
LOCATION:Houston Run Complex\, 835 Houston Run Dr\, Gap\, 17527
CATEGORIES:Amish,Fairs & Festivals,Food & Beverage Events,Mud Sales,Southern Lancaster
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://lancasterpa.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/gap-fire-company-feature-buggies.jpg
END:VEVENT
