SUMMARY:Farmersville Volunteer Fire Co. Sale
DESCRIPTION:Date for Mud Sale Friday\, March 27th\, 2026\nORDER OF SALE: Inside @ 4:30\, Outside @ 5:00 Shrubbery @ approx. 5:30 Quilts @ approx. 7:00\nCash or good PA check — Delicious food served by the Farmersville Ladies Auxiliary \nFarmersville Fire Co is still accepting Quality Donations/Consignments for this year’s Auction\nFor more information or items for auction please call 717-490-4487 or 717-354-5094\n[No Sunday Calls Please]\nNo Pets\, tires or hazardous items! Not responsible for accidents \nSale Committee reserves the right to refuse any all items. This is a no reserve auction. \n  \n\nMud Sales are a unique Lancaster County tradition to raise funds for local volunteer fire companies. See our complete schedule of Lancaster County mud sales. \nPlease Note: Many of the Fire Companies holding mud sales can always use extra help on the days they receive items and the day of the event.  It takes a LOT of labor to put on a mud sale.
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/farmersville-volunteer-fire-co-sale/
