SUMMARY:Spring Greening the Lower Susquehanna - Treelay! Tree Planting and Live Staking
DESCRIPTION:Greening the Lower Susquehanna is partnering with Lancaster Farmacy\, the Chesapeake Bay Foundation and the Alliance for the Chesapeake Bay to host a planting as part of Treelay- the Alliance’s 4th  annual watershed-wide hands-on volunteer day. We will be planting trees and live stakes to reduce erosion and to fill in empty areas and expand the existing forest. This is a big project and we can use lots of hands! \n\n\nRegister here. 
