SUMMARY:Egg Hunt & Bunny Breakfast
DESCRIPTION:The Relay For Life of Lancaster County and the Church of the Apostles UCC invite you to the Easter Egg Hunt\, Breakfast & Spring Vendor Market!  \nSchedule of the day: \n\nDoors open at 8:45am\nEgg hunt starts promptly at 9am\nBreakfast: 9am – 11am\nSpring Vendor Market: 9am – 12pm\nEaster Bunny arrives at 9:30am\nPhotos with the Easter Bunny\,  and kids crafts: 9:30am – 12pm\nRaffles 9am – 11:30am\nRaffle Winners announced at 12pm\n\nLearn More & Get Your Tickets: Easter Egg Hunt\, Breakfast & Spring Vendor Market
URL:https://apostlesucc.org/event/egg-hunt-bunny-breakfast/
LOCATION:Church of the Apostles UCC\, 1850 Marietta Ave\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17603\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://apostlesucc.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Breakfast_w_Easter_Bunny_Flyer-11.jpg
