SUMMARY:Galactic Forces: A Sci-Fi Celebration
DESCRIPTION:Galactic Forces\nJoin us on Saturday\, March 28th\, from 10 am – 2 pm\, as we celebrate all things Sci-Fi (emphasis on the science)! We encourage you to dress up as your favorite sci-fi characters while learning about the science of forces in our exhibit hall and with special hands-on activities.  Who knows\, you may see some special visitors from a galaxy far\, far away while you explore! \nThis event is presented free with admission. Purchasing tickets in advance is encouraged\, but tickets will also be available at the door. Members and those using free-admission programs should not purchase tickets in advance. \nClick here to buy advance tickets for Saturday\, March 28th. 
URL:https://lancastersciencefactory.org/event/galactic-forces-a-sci-fi-celebration/
LOCATION:The Lancaster Science Factory\, 454 New Holland Ave\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17602\, United States
CATEGORIES:Educational Programs,Special Programs
