DESCRIPTION:We love democracy. We love crafts. We love snacks. And we love
  civic engagement. You too? Join us for **Anti-Fascist Craft Night** in Li
 titz—a low-key hang where we cut up cereal boxes and old magazines\, mak
 e wild collage postcards and letters\, and send our thoughts (and shade) t
 o our elected officials. Make your voice heard in a weirdly therapeutic an
 d hands-on way! **What to bring:** * Clean cardboard (cereal/snack boxes) 
 or card stock * Old magazines\, catalogs\, newspapers\, greeting cards\, e
 tc
