BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Amtshows": "https://amtshows.com/show/the-simon-garfunkel-story-2026/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:amtshows
X-SOURCE:Amtshows
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260402T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260402T193000
DTSTAMP:20260313T235930
CREATED:20250804T133014Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251204T174143Z
UID:10001801-1775158200-1775158200@amtshows.com
SUMMARY:The Simon & Garfunkel Story
DESCRIPTION:Tickets: $39 $49 $59 $69 \nVIP 1&2: The Simon & Garfunkel Story VIP Experience  $172-$182 \nThe Simon & Garfunkel Story VIP Experience Includes: \n\nOne Ticket with in the first 10 rows\nA private 20-minute acoustic performance with the lead performers of The Simon & Garfunkel Story for VIP attendees only\, featuring exclusive Simon & Garfunkel songs not performed in the main show. “Stripped back\, with one guitar and two voices… singing in harmony.”\nA Meet & Greet and photo opportunity with the two lead performers of The Simon & Garfunkel Story.\nA limited edition\, collectible VIP laminate.\n\nVIP UPGRADE: The Simon & Garfunkel Story VIP Experience Upgrade $113  \nThe Simon & Garfunkel Story VIP Experience Upgrade* Includes: \n\nA private 20-minute acoustic performance with the lead performers of The Simon & Garfunkel Story for VIP attendees only\, featuring exclusive Simon & Garfunkel songs not performed in the main show. “Stripped back\, with one guitar and two voices… singing in harmony.”\nA Meet & Greet and photo opportunity with the two lead performers of The Simon & Garfunkel Story.\nA limited edition\, collectible VIP laminate.\n\n*Upgrade packages DO NOT INCLUDE TICKETS. A ticket is required to enter the venue. \nNow seen in 50 countries worldwide\, The Simon and Garfunkel Story is a critically acclaimed concert style theatre show about two young boys from Queens\, New York who went on to become the world’s most successful music duo of all time.  Using state of the art video projection\, incredible lighting\, and a full live band\, The Simon & Garfunkel Story is a moving and powerful concert featuring all the hits such as “Mrs. Robinson\,” “Bridge Over Troubled Water\,” “Homeward Bound\,” “Scarborough Fair\,” “The Boxer\,” “The Sound Of Silence\,” and many more. \nFor certain concerts\, audience members may prefer to stand or dance\, especially when encouraged by the artist to do so. Guest expectations differ\, so we simply ask all attendees to extend mutual respect toward one another and maintain awareness of those around them. Our staff will only intervene in matters of safety or when behavior is deemed unruly\, combative\, or disruptive to the overall performance.
URL:https://amtshows.com/show/the-simon-garfunkel-story-2026/
LOCATION:American Music Theatre\, 2425 Lincoln Hwy East\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17605\, United States
CATEGORIES:Celebrity Concerts
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://amtshows.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/SG_Concessions-Events-and-News-for-Website-1920x1080-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
