SUMMARY:Good Friday Service
DESCRIPTION:We invite you to join us on April 3rd at 7 PM in the Sanctuary for our Good Friday service. Together\, we will hold space for prayer and reflection as we remember the ultimate sacrifice of Christ’s love. \n“For God so loved the world that he gave his one and only Son\, that whoever believes in him shall not perish but have eternal life.” — John 3:16 \nWhether you wish to participate in the service or simply sit in quiet observation\, please know that all are welcome here.
