SUMMARY:2746 - Easter Pastries: Make and Take
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Easter with a hands-on family friendly pastry class focused on seasonal baking techniques and traditional holiday treats. Under the guidance of Chef Sophia Dickmyer\, guests will work with enriched doughs and classic fillings while learning shaping\, proofing\, and finishing methods perfect for spring celebrations. Each guest will leave with freshly baked pastries to enjoy at home for Easter breakfast. \nHands on. Ages 12 and up. Guests under the age of 16 must attend with a ticketed adult. \n\nHot Cross Buns\nLemon Blueberry Muffins\nEaster Bunny Twists\nNutella Egg Nests
