DESCRIPTION:Join us for a hands-on artisanal pizza class with Chef Sophia Dickmyer. Learn the fundamentals of great pizza making\, from dough mixing and fermentation to shaping and baking for the perfect crust. Explore how simple\, high-quality ingredients and thoughtful techniques come together to create exceptional pizza from scratch. \nHands on. BYOB. Ages 16 and up. Vegetarian friendly* \n\nPizza Dough \nMarinara from Scratch\nClassic Margarita \nRicotta\, Prosciutto and Arugula White Pizza\nS’mores Dessert Pizza
