DESCRIPTION:The Compassion Team invites you to a monthly Spiritual Support Group on Second Thursdays\, from 10-11 AM in the Compassion Corner (Room 107). \nThis small\, caring group offers a confidential space to share joys and burdens\, reflect with a short devotion\, and pray for one another. All are welcome to find encouragement\, connection\, and rest in God’s presence.
