DESCRIPTION:Celebrate seasonal Spring ingredients in this hands-on farm-to-table cooking class with Chef Josh Noll. Guests will learn how to work with fresh\, locally sourced produce and thoughtfully selected ingredients while exploring techniques that highlight natural flavors. This class focuses on ingredient-driven cooking\, simple preparations\, and building balanced dishes that let the season shine. \nHands on. BYOB. Ages 21 and up. Tickets are priced per person. \n\nSweet Pea Risotto\nPan-Seared Scallops\nLemon Garlic Butter Sauce\nWild Arugula Salad\nFrench 75
