UID:10001847-1775935800-1775935800@amtshows.com
SUMMARY:An Evening of Alton Brown
DESCRIPTION:Tickets: $64 $74 $84 \nVIP: Alton Brown VIP Experience: $200 \nIncludes: \n\nOne ticket for admission\nA special VIP experience one hour before show time.\nIt will include a brief Q&A session in the Theatre.\nA signed copy of Alton’s book.\n\n*There will be no individual photos or autographs\, however\, photos will be allowed during the experience.  Video is strictly prohibited. \n*If you purchase a VIP Experience\, AMT will notify you by email prior to the event to give you additional instructions. \nAlthough he’s keeping the details under wraps\, Brown has said that with An Evening of Alton Brown he’s “stirring up some twists on his greatest hits\,” and “spicing things up with new demonstrations\, music\, and slightly scaled-down mayhem.”  No matter what\, An Evening of Alton Brown will present Brown as you’ve never seen him — unless\, of course\, you’ve been invited to his house. \nBest known for creating and hosting groundbreaking television such as Good Eats\, Iron Chef America\, Cutthroat Kitchen\, and Food Network Star\, Brown has also built one of the most successful culinary touring franchises ever\, performing live in more than 300 cities for well over half a million fans. With An Evening of Alton Brown\, he strips away the spectacle in favor of connection\, spontaneity\, and storytelling\, delivering a show that is equal parts humor\, science\, food\, and heart. \nFor certain concerts\, audience members may prefer to stand or dance\, especially when encouraged by the artist to do so. Guest expectations differ\, so we simply ask all attendees to extend mutual respect toward one another and maintain awareness of those around them. Our staff will only intervene in matters of safety or when behavior is deemed unruly\, combative\, or disruptive to the overall performance.
URL:https://amtshows.com/show/alton-brown/
LOCATION:American Music Theatre\, 2425 Lincoln Hwy East\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17605\, United States
CATEGORIES:Celebrity Concerts
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://amtshows.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/AB_Concessions-Events-and-News-for-Website-1920x1080-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
