SUMMARY:2751 - Tropical Latin Flavors
DESCRIPTION:Escape to the tropics in this hands-on cooking class with Chef Flora Gonzalez. Guests will explore bright\, sunny flavors and techniques inspired by Latin and island cuisines while learning how to balance sweet\, savory\, and citrus elements. This class focuses on working with fresh ingredients\, building layered flavors\, and creating vibrant dishes that feel both playful and approachable. \nHands on. BYOB. Ages 16 and up.  Gluten Free \n\nFresh Pineapple Stuffed with Coconut Shrimp Fried Rice\nBright Pineapple Salsa with Citrus & Fresh Herbs\nLimber de Coco (Tropical Frozen Dessert)
URL:https://zestchef.com/class/2751-tropical-latin-flavors/
LOCATION:Zest Cooking School\, 1180 Erbs Quarry Road\, Lititz\, PA\, 17543\, United States
CATEGORIES:Gluten Free,International Cuisine,Seasonal
