X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_scrapandcraft
X-SOURCE:Meetup Scrapandcraft
UID:event_xvnsvqyjcgbcc@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260314T040025Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260421T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260421T220000
SUMMARY:Lancaster Scrapbooking & Papercrafting Monthly gathering
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Scrapbooking\, Cards & Papercrafts\nScrapbook\, make
  cards\, practice quilling\, or paint!\nMeeting on the third Tuesday\, 6-1
 0 p.m.\, at the Cozy Crop House. (Also meeting the next night\, Wednesday\
 , same time & place. You can come to one or both\, and can leave your gear
  overnight.) A chance to meet & gather monthly with local scrapbookers & c
 rafters\, in an ideal crafting environment! Plenty of room to do your own 
 thing while we socialize. Bring your own supplies & projects\, or just sit
  back and relax with scrapping friends\, and watch & learn a new technique
 .\nSpecific crafting events (eg. card classes\, paint nights\, etc) may be
  featured here as scheduled.\nBring snacks to share if you wish.\nMeetup g
 roups are charged a monthly administration fee which is currently paid in 
 this group by a few members. VOLUNTARY donations of $1 or $2 into a group 
 "kitty" will help us continue the group's open membership and online adver
 tising. The rate it costs our _whole group_ is about $12/month for a 6-mon
 th commitment. Please do not feel you cannot come if you don't contribute-
 -the fee is paid\, and donations are voluntary to cover future fees.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/scrapandcraft/events/xvnsvqyjcgbcc/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20190405T040038Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20190405T040038Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
