DESCRIPTION:Step into the comfort and charm of rustic French cooking in this hands-on class with Chef Sophia Dickmyer. Inspired by traditional countryside kitchens\, this class focuses on simple techniques\, seasonal ingredients\, and the kind of cooking meant to be shared around the table. \nHands on. BYOB. Ages 16 and up. \n\nGougers (cheese puffs)\nBeef Bourguignon\nPommes Puree (whipped garlic potatoes)\nCaramel Apple Galette with Mascarpone Whipped Cream 
