SUMMARY:2758 - Spring Cheesecakes
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate the flavors of spring in this hands-on baking class with Pastry Chef Faith Kennedy. Guests will learn the fundamentals of creating smooth\, balanced cheesecakes while exploring lighter\, seasonal flavor combinations. This class focuses on techniques\, from mixing and baking to finishing and presentation\, giving you the confidence to recreate beautiful cheesecakes at home for any spring gathering. \nHands on. BYOB. Ages 16 and up. Vegetarian. Gluten Free \n\nLemon Ricotta Cheesecake\nMini Brown Butter and Vanilla Bean cheesecake\nPistachio Basque Cheesecake
URL:https://zestchef.com/class/2758-spring-cheesecakes/
LOCATION:Zest Cooking School\, 1180 Erbs Quarry Road\, Lititz\, PA\, 17543\, United States
CATEGORIES:Basics and Techniques,Dessert,Gluten Free,Let's Bake,Vegetarian
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://zestchef.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/cheesecakes-spring-2026-e1771372249664.jpg
END:VEVENT
