SUMMARY:Energy Healing Hour with Anna
DESCRIPTION:Being One Center in Lancaster County\nJoin Anna for a relaxing
  hour of energy healing\, releasing Energy Blockages\, and Reinvigorate yo
 ur chakras.\n\nEveryone needs to take more time self-care in these transfo
 rmational times! Gift yourself one hour to let go and receive.\n\nEnergy h
 ealing will occur when you open yourself to receiving the loving energy of
  the universe from your Oneness Consciousness.\n\nEveryone who is attendin
 g will receive a remote energy healing transmission and experience a guide
 d meditation.\n\nThis Event is lovingly hosted By Anna Bojczuk— a Regist
 ered nurse with over 40 years of experience and a gifted Energy worker. An
 na is also a long-time volunteer and inspiration in the Being One Center C
 ommunity.\n\nSuggested Donation $10\nTo Donate Visit: www.beingonecenter.o
 rg/support
