DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260619T073000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260619T083000
SUMMARY:Data Lancaster Coffee Meetup
DESCRIPTION:Data Lancaster\nWe meet up at the Mean Cup coffee shop and cha
 t about whatever topics come to mind. Attendees tend to work in data-relat
 ed jobs\, so expect at least some data-related discussions\, and attendees
  sharing what they've been up to on the data-related projects they're work
 ing on is common.\n\nBe sure to join the Data Lancaster Meetup group in or
 der to receive notifications of future events!\n\n*(And if you have a conf
 lict this month and want to plan for the future\, we meet the third Friday
  of the month every month except November and December)*
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/data-lancaster/events/312776831/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260108T003858Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260108T003858Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Bird In Hand": "https://bird-in-hand.com/event/lancaster-county-benefit-auction-3/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:bird_in_hand
X-SOURCE:Bird In Hand
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260620
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260621
DTSTAMP:20260313T235924
CREATED:20260309T112645Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260309T112645Z
UID:10001056-1781913600-1781999999@bird-in-hand.com
SUMMARY:Lancaster County Benefit Auction
DESCRIPTION:Experience the vibrant spirit of the annual Lancaster County Benefit Auction\, a day where community fellowship meets the thrill of the auction block. This local tradition brings people together for a memorable experience filled with lively bidding and incredible food\, all organized to benefit families facing rare genetic disorders at the Clinic for Special Children. \nThe auction features an expansive array of goods ranging from traditional carriages and carts to masterfully crafted quilts and household furniture. Attendees can browse a massive inventory of farm supplies\, hardware\, and professional-grade tools\, alongside outdoor furniture and a lush selection of shrubbery and plants. Whether you are searching for rare collectibles\, children’s toys\, or beautifully arranged theme baskets\, the variety ensures there is something for every interest.
URL:https://bird-in-hand.com/event/lancaster-county-benefit-auction-3/
LOCATION:Leola Produce Auction\, 135 Brethren Church Road\, Leola\, PA\, 17540\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bird-in-hand.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/BenefitAuction.jpg
END:VEVENT
