SUMMARY:Wednesday night Meetup
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Scrapbooking\, Cards & Papercrafts\nA second night t
 o finish up what you started Tuesday\, or a chance to make it if Tuesday d
 oesn't work for you! [i]PLEASE R.S.V.P. and if your plans change\, come ba
 ck to CHANGE THE R.S.V.P. We have limited spaces available\, and a "yes" R
 .S.V.P. can eliminate a spot for someone else.[/i] Same times and location
  as Tuesday meetups (Cozy Crop House\, 6-10 p.m.)\, scheduled to be the We
 dnesday after our Tuesday meetups -- usually the third Wednesday of the mo
 nth.
