UID:10001474-1793984400-1793991600@lancastersciencefactory.org
SUMMARY:First Friday @ The Lancaster Science Factory!
DESCRIPTION:Every First Friday the Lancaster Science Factory offers free admission from 5 – 7pm for the first 300 guests. Explore over 80 interactive exhibits for kids in grades K – 8 and their families! This program is possible through the generous support of PPL. \n  \nCHILDREN MUST BE ACCOMPANIED BY AN ADULT
